metadata.name: Undead Ape Gen2 #1
metadata.description: A collection of 6,666 Gen2 Undead Apes have risen from the dead! With over 200 hand-drawn traits and billions of combinations possible, each Undead Ape in the collection is truly unique. By including only desirable traits and with our artist's careful eye to detail and aesthetic, there are no floor apes here! From the ashes rise a collection of inclusive, affordable, and good-looking apes. More than a PFP, each ape represents a unique individual in our community-driven, multi-gender, exquisitely curated project with insane art, strong camaraderie, and a willingness to adjust to our family's needs. This is the Undead Ape Society.
